data.description: Ring in the new year with this PERFECT starter home or RENTAL opportunity under $250,000! This 2 Bedroom 2 Bathroom 1 Car Garage home is completely updated and right under 1,000 square feet. You will love how the living room has lots of natural light which is warm and welcoming. The entire home has been tastefully updated and is completely move in ready! The open floor plan leads you to the kitchen which has been updated with white shaker cabinets including soft close feature, granite counters and stainless steel appliances! The dining room is just off from the kitchen which is perfect for your family gatherings. Both bedrooms have nice size cedar closets and plenty of space for a king size bed. The garage features a separate bathroom with toilet and shower but no sink. The backyard is very peaceful and private with no backyard neighbors and views of conservation. The roof and A/C were both replaced in 2014.  ALL FURNITURE CONVEYS WITH THE HOME WITH THE EXCEPTION OF THE PICTURES AND A FEW DECORATIONS <<SHORT TERM RENTALS AND AIR BNB IS ALLOWED with no restrictions>> Home is located minutes to the Veterans Expressway and 20 minutes to the beautiful beaches!
